snippet.title: Woolfe - The Red Hood Diaries - Release Trailer 2015
snippet.description:
Woolfe - The Red Hood Diaries
http://play.WoolfeGame.com
A twisted fable in a rich, fantasy setting of smoke-spewing factories and evil forests, Woolfe: The Red Hood Diaries is an action-platforming fairy tale of death, industrial greed and vengeance.
